■ Choose a bet amount and place your bet, 
then the F-35A will take off.

■ The longer the F-35A flies, the higher the multiplier, 
and the greater the winnings.

■ Press Stop before the F-35A flies away
to cash out your winnings.
■ Select Auto Bet to place bets continuously for multiple rounds.

■ Select Auto Stop and set an auto-stop multiplier to stop
automatically without manual action.

■ The jackpot is triggered when the crash multiplier consists
of identical even numbers (both decimal digits are the same,
and all digits before the decimal point are also the same),
and the multiplier is greater than 4.00x.

■ The jackpot is triggered when the crash multiplier consists
of identical odd numbers (both decimal digits are the same, 
and all digits before the decimal point are also the same),
and the multiplier is greater than 4.00x.

■ After the Even Jackpot is triggered, 
the Odd Jackpot will appear, and vice versa.
■ Cash-out multiplier must be 2.00x or higher

■ The jackpot payout is calculated based on bet amount and
cash-out multiplier using one of the following formulas:

0.6 × Jackpot Amount × Bet Amount

(0.4 × Jackpot Amount × Cash-out Multiplier) ÷

(Total Bet Amount ÷ Total Cash-out Multiplier)

■ Jackpots may appear randomly and may disappear\r\n
after being triggered.
